&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m trying to execute a simple MySQL query as below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-sql s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; user_details (username, location, key)
&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&apos;Tim&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&apos;Florida&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But I&apos;m getting the following error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;ERROR 1064 (42000): You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MySQL server version for the right syntax to use near &lt;code&gt;&apos;key) VALUES (&apos;Tim&apos;, &apos;Florida&apos;, 42)&apos;&lt;/code&gt; at line 1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How can I fix the issue?&lt;/p&gt;
